Distributed Dictionary

The server is implemented in Java - UDPServer.java and the Client is implemented in both java and python (UDPClient.java and UDPCient.py)


Dictionary.java validates the word and gets the meaning from dictionary.txt

To Run Server - 

Copy Dictionary.java and UDPServer.java to any IDE (eclipse, IntelliJ etc..) and run UDPServer 

Use java 1.8


To Run Client

Python UDPClient.py


Note - type in "#" from client to end the session